{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "HZOYBC2UVQIFPDIPCCBQEPSCAMEH2P7F",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "809006001",
    "title": "樫本流、片付け術",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "研修や会議が重なり、バタバタとした\r\n日々が続いたある日。ひと息ついていると――",
            "enText": "One day, after a hectic day of training \nand meetings, I took a break. I \nwas taking a break…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "pathId": 5018377679881044719,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "この部屋、なぜこんなに荒れているのですか。\r\n溜まったほこり、ゴミ、積まれた書類……！",
            "enText": "Why is this room in such a state of \ndisrepair? The accumulated dust, the \nrubbish, the piles of papers…!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 313,
                    "pathId": -3105667041519401722
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": -2393794460196036536
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 524673544103704691,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "配布物を渡したらすぐ仕事に戻るつもり\r\nでしたが……予定を変更します。",
            "enText": "I was going to go back to work as soon as I \nhad handed out the handouts, but I have \nchanged my plans to…",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -5172619533404344822
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": -4688442330062843966
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1066890429359535518,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "部屋の乱れは心の乱れ。\r\n手伝いますから、今すぐ掃除しますよ。",
            "enText": "A messy room is a messy mind. I'll help you, \nI'll clean it right now.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 116304263200976554
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -5378411128586939928
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4106645386347664367,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "急遽、マンツーマンお掃除教室が始まった。",
            "enText": "A one-to-one cleaning class \nwas suddenly started.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": 8469635773506238609
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 123,
                    "pathId": -6997847505676964993
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5215082891846838102,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "窓は開けなさい、ゴミ袋を用意！\r\nまずは机の上から整理します！",
            "enText": "Windows open, rubbish bags at the ready! \nOrganise your desk first!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 1909058702483609251
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -2717774153350987223
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7424937438786628228,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "不要な物は捨てる！　細かい物はまとめる！\r\n……クリップをバラで引き出しに入れるな！",
            "enText": "Throw away what you don't need! Put the \nsmall stuff together! Don't put… clips in \nthe drawer in pieces!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": 8044958531805921776
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 110,
                    "pathId": 7897877088458426643
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5300295702357560397,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そんな、厳しくも的確な指示のおかげで、\r\n掃除は手際よく進み――",
            "enText": "Thanks to her strict but precise \ninstructions, the cleaning went very well.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -4384455523165712023
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 7736399485723070891
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3194326017472481911,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "はぁ……。あらかた整理できましたね。\r\n残るは、ゴミ捨てと書類の整理ですか。",
            "enText": "Huh… So, you've sorted it all out. The only \nthing left to do is to throw away the \nrubbish and sort out the paperwork.",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 94,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 274,
                    "pathId": -1079504029702383848
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 146,
                    "pathId": 5848061173620486273
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7659407723979826327,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "ここまできたら最後まで手伝いましょう。\r\nどちらか請け負います。",
            "enText": "If you've made it this far, we'll help you \nfinish. We'll take on one of you.",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ゴミ捨てをお願いします",
                    "enText": "Please take out the rubbish",
                    "nextBlock": 11
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "書類の整理をお願いします",
                    "enText": "Organise your paperwork, please.",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": -1241185502212040372
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 6400195519509184822
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -147686461261345605,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "わかりました。……念のため\r\n準備運動をしてから取りかかります。",
            "enText": "Yes, I know… I'll do some prep work just to \nbe sure before I start.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 451399406036610066
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -8520815434851686729
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": -8994318673628139871
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7514600055936914644,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "……くっ……！\r\nなんの、これしき……！",
            "enText": "Stick to…! What the hell is this…!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -438439935596408950
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -8208737374231758589
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 62404237008946752,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そんなこんなで、トレーナー室は\r\n綺麗に片づいた。",
            "enText": "The trainer's room is now clean and tidy.",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "ありがとうございました！",
                    "enText": "Thank you very much!",
                    "nextBlock": 14
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 234,
                    "pathId": 4493538967721242196
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 189,
                    "pathId": 3233617935146716701
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6339305061901905136,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "構いません。同じ学園に勤めるものとして、\r\n協力し合うのは当然です。では、私はこれで。",
            "enText": "That's fine. It is only right that we work \ntogether as colleagues in the same school. \nI'll leave you to it.",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 1699789599326395606
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 234,
                    "pathId": -686109414077980469
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 6424586827537218334
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 387439032723617464,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "……明日は筋肉痛になりそうだな……。",
            "enText": "… I'm going to have sore muscles tomorrow…",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 68,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -4690026739028845375
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 4704494017400548687
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8872548489783505386,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "わかりました。整理は得意な方ですが……\r\nこの量は骨が折れそうです。",
            "enText": "I understand. I'm good at organising, but … \nthis amount of work is daunting.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -2433331879495149565
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 190,
                    "pathId": 901528382351623907
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 360332528858307585
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5528824199609716791,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "必要、不要、不明、不要、必要、不明。\r\nわかってはいたが、多いな……。",
            "enText": "Necessary, unnecessary, unknown, \nunnecessary, necessary, unknown. I knew it, \nbut there's a lot of it…",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 8214253650992776891
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5377798037630297201
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7670192574165846091,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "……こんなにも時間がかかるとは。そろそろ\r\n紙媒体での情報共有廃止を検討すべきですね。",
            "enText": "… I didn't realise it would take so long. I \nthink it's time to consider abolishing \npaper-based information sharing.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 196,
                    "pathId": -3353841564467943712
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": -951731726661285143
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1065562466604064167,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "樫本理子",
            "enName": "Kashimoto Riko",
            "jpText": "ここでの経験を、URA上層部に報告しても？",
            "enText": "May I report my experience here \nto the URA senior management?",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 72,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -3747185168127397140
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 83,
                    "pathId": -2708034799215935550
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8611658913640423841,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "数日後、紙媒体での情報共有についての\r\nアンケートが回ってきたのだった。",
            "enText": "A few days later, a questionnaire \nwas circulated about sharing information \nin paper form.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 146,
                    "pathId": -7138080577136237902
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 153,
                    "pathId": 1117104547675808501
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6570519201154067018,
            "blockIdx": 20
        }
    ],
    "modified": 1669946289
}